DESCRIPTION:ROLLY IN THE DARK // THE ONLY STREETLAMP  ROLLY IN THE DARK Since 2019\, RITD has been crafting a distinctive blend of southern gothic storytelling\, haunted folk atmosphere\, and dark country roots\, with songs that feel like midnight stories told around a fire. Led by Rolly’s powerful voice\, the mournful poetic lyrics are evoking haunted landscapes\, the magic of the night\, the inner fire and the inner demons\, devils and ghosts\, and tales of souls who resist and transform\, like old burned witches returning to claim their feminist liberation. Combining older compositions written over two decades ago with newly created material\, the band’s fresh lineup marks an exciting new phase in their ongoing (r)evolution. Rolly – Vocals\, Acoustic Guitar\, Banjolele Fabian – Acoustic Guitar Jackson – Double Bass Lizzy – Violin https://linktr.ee/rollyinthedark… THE ONLY STREETLAMP An independent musical project/band formed by a piano and guitar player and singer-songwriter from British Columbia\, Canada\, who is heavily connected to the Austrian music scene.The Only Streetlamp blends acoustic pop\, folk\, and indie rock elements. While rooted in Canada\, the artist has spent significant time in Austria for gigs\, touring\, and busking. https://open.spotify.com/artist/093bf453FoetDW2NR6ssZ4… New album expected on July 3rd\, 2026 Be there at 20:00 Entry: Donation
URL:https://www.cafe-carina.at/2020/events/rolly-in-the-dark-the-only-streetlamp/
END:VEVENT
